{"tid":640327,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【苦幹】挑戰三十日慢寫。從樣衰潦草到筆走龍蛇。","createTime":"2018-04-24T08:11:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T09:21:26.000Z","uid":64971,"like":22,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"ea19dc5b43b1f79a66f6eb9977ddcf73ac4ca5ed","tid":640327,"uid":64971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T08:11:17.000Z","msg":"Hi, 我叫白熊。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <strong>點解要練字？ </strong><br />\n<br />\n1. 坊間大量求職求學Written/Exam/Cert/jre/cre 都仍然係以手寫英文為主，所以或者手字好，廢青都當寶。<br />\n<br />\n2. 練字如打座、唸經、畫畫，可平靜心靈，有助思考。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <strong>打算點練法？</strong><br />\n<br />\n慢慢寫，三十日期間一直交待進度。紀錄亦會係我的個人Blog 更新。白熊紳士咖啡廳<a href=\"http://mrpolarbear.blog\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fmrpolarbear.blog&d=6rgDRqZdkloq1MaO0jNX42owyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=4e262dbb\" target=\"_blank\">mrpolarbear.blog</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><strong> 你練關我咩事？</strong><br />\n<br />\n如你手字比我樣衰： 無得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n如你手字同我差唔多：不妨今日開始一齊寫，互相鼓勵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如你手字好過我：不妨食花生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如你係手寫大師： 請自貼幫下所有有需要既巴絲。<br />\n<br />\n最後，自我介紹一下，我叫白熊，係一個在職的90後。<br />\n由今日起開始計三十日，每日寫字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一個月後，收成正果。"},{"pid":"c592b3bf17cdc7bf6becbe603936de5536784c06","tid":640327,"uid":69221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T08:13:39.000Z","msg":"留名學寫字"},{"pid":"9958ffc6bcfb0098bc4498542b3e268e608e4d9a","tid":640327,"uid":149664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-24T08:16:14.000Z","msg":"留名<br />\n利申：小學雞字"},{"pid":"d8b2528c5fb7e30119a4e514cfc292a86e01e633","tid":640327,"uid":64971,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"cit